00:26:34,688 --> 00:26:36,688
that his father is a murderer.

576
00:26:38,847 --> 00:26:40,448
How is my child going to carry on
with his life?

577
00:26:41,968 --> 00:26:43,407
How are my wife and child

578
00:26:43,407 --> 00:26:44,288
going to carry on with their lives?

579
00:26:48,367 --> 00:26:49,528
Is this the truth

580
00:26:49,728 --> 00:26:51,008
that you reporters want?

581
00:27:05,448 --> 00:27:07,407
It's too late for everything now.

582
00:27:11,008 --> 00:27:12,327
I made the mistake myself.

583
00:27:14,392 --> 00:27:16,167
I'll atone for my sin.

584
00:27:26,928 --> 00:27:28,887
Please don't die.

585
00:28:04,610 --> 00:28:12,660
(Emergency)

586
00:28:12,928 --> 00:28:13,448
(Xu Lai.)

587
00:28:14,327 --> 00:28:15,887
(Because of Wang Yi's suicidal attempt)

588
00:28:16,127 --> 00:28:16,968
(and his wife's pre-term labor,)

589
00:28:17,607 --> 00:28:19,288
(the netizens are pointing fingers
at you now.)

590
00:28:19,887 --> 00:28:21,127
(They accused the reporter
of publishing the article)

591
00:28:21,407 --> 00:28:22,367
(to seek attention,)

592
00:28:22,567 --> 00:28:23,928
(despite knowing that the director)

593
00:28:24,208 --> 00:28:25,528
(was willing to take responsibility,)

594
00:28:26,008 --> 00:28:27,127
(causing his family to fall apart.)

595
00:28:28,167 --> 00:28:30,167
(The situation isn't favorable for you.)

596
00:28:30,768 --> 00:28:31,688
(Take a few days off and rest.)

597
00:28:38,288 --> 00:28:39,847
I'm sorry. I should've come earlier.

598
00:28:41,248 --> 00:28:42,327
Liu Xu has told me everything.

599
00:28:44,167 --> 00:28:45,248
Don't be afraid. I'm here with you.

600
00:28:55,928 --> 00:28:56,607
How's Wang Yi now?

601
00:28:57,248 --> 00:28:58,488
What about his wife and baby?

602
00:28:59,488 --> 00:29:00,528
He fell from a height.

603
00:29:00,807 --> 00:29:02,567
Although there was an air cushion
to cushion the impact,

604
00:29:03,327 --> 00:29:05,448
the pressure has inflicted

605
00:29:05,448 --> 00:29:07,647
on his body in different extent.

606
00:29:08,887 --> 00:29:10,407
Luckily, he has been saved.

607
00:29:10,968 --> 00:29:11,688
But he remains

608
00:29:11,688 --> 00:29:12,688
in critical condition now.

609
00:29:12,807 --> 00:29:13,688
We need further observation.

610
00:29:14,248 --> 00:29:16,807
He might suffer the aftereffect.

611
00:29:18,048 --> 00:29:19,087
As for his wife and baby,

612
00:29:19,288 --> 00:29:20,048
I've asked about them.

613
00:29:21,288 --> 00:29:22,208
The baby is saved.

614
00:29:23,127 --> 00:29:24,448
But since it's just seven months old,

615
00:29:24,728 --> 00:29:25,887
they keep it in an incubator

616
00:29:25,887 --> 00:29:26,607
for further observation.

617
00:29:27,048 --> 00:29:30,167
However, his wife has a terrible mental state.

618
00:29:54,688 --> 00:29:55,127
Xu Lai.

619
00:30:00,928 --> 00:30:02,087
I want some time alone.

620
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:12,310
(Outpatient Department)

621
00:30:17,248 --> 00:30:18,327
Because of your report,

622
00:30:18,728 --> 00:30:19,928
Wang Yi wanted to commit suicide

623
00:30:20,087 --> 00:30:21,367
and now no one takes care
of the nursing home.

624
00:30:21,688 --> 00:30:24,087
What are we going to do now?

625
00:30:24,087 --> 00:30:25,847
You shouldn't have meddled.

626
00:30:25,968 --> 00:30:27,448
Old people like us have to suffer now

627
00:30:28,208 --> 00:30:29,847
because of you.

628
00:30:30,288 --> 00:30:31,167
Compensate our loss!

629
00:30:31,327 --> 00:30:32,327
Compensate our loss!

630
00:30:34,167 --> 00:30:34,928
Ms. Xu.

631
00:30:36,367 --> 00:30:37,768
We don't blame you.

632
00:30:37,887 --> 00:30:38,567
We all know

633
00:30:39,048 --> 00:30:40,528
you sympathized with Ms. Zheng.

634
00:30:40,688 --> 00:30:42,367
But we have no choice.

635
00:30:43,048 --> 00:30:44,567
Now that the director had an accident,

636
00:30:44,728 --> 00:30:45,728
and the nursing home

637
00:30:45,728 --> 00:30:48,288
can't be rebuilt soon.

638
00:30:48,807 --> 00:30:51,167
We can't just stay

639
00:30:51,167 --> 00:30:53,208
in the temporary shelter for long.

640
00:30:54,688 --> 00:30:55,607
Ms. Xu.

641
00:30:55,807 --> 00:30:58,688
We're done.

642
00:30:59,127 --> 00:30:59,928
What should we do now?

643
00:31:02,607 --> 00:31:03,327
Excuse me.

644
00:31:03,327 --> 00:31:03,928
Make ways, please.

645
00:31:03,928 --> 00:31:04,448
Make ways.

646
00:31:04,448 --> 00:31:05,208
Please help us.

647
00:31:07,327 --> 00:31:08,048
Don't go!

648
00:31:09,288 --> 00:31:10,728
What should we do now?

649
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,180
(You've disgraced the profession.)

650
00:31:24,180 --> 00:31:28,410
(Unconscionable reporter!
Get out of the TV station!)

651
00:31:28,410 --> 00:31:32,530
(How can you be so cruel?!
Unconscionable reporter!)

652
00:31:39,407 --> 00:31:39,968
It's okay.

653
00:31:40,728 --> 00:31:41,367
Don't look at them.

654
00:32:09,928 --> 00:32:10,607
I'm dirty.

655
00:32:11,087 --> 00:32:11,928
I need a shower.

656
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:38,060
(Liar!)

657
00:33:22,567 --> 00:33:23,887
Is this the truth

658
00:33:24,008 --> 00:33:25,647
you reporters want?

659
00:33:25,847 --> 00:33:26,327
(Unconscionable reporter.)

660
00:33:26,688 --> 00:33:27,607
(Your report almost killed someone.)

661
00:33:27,607 --> 00:33:28,127
(That's right.)

662
00:33:28,127 --> 00:33:28,567
(No one knows)

663
00:33:28,567 --> 00:33:29,528
(when the nursing home will be rebuilt.)

664
00:33:29,567 --> 00:33:30,528
(What about the elderly?)

665
00:33:30,607 --> 00:33:31,607
(You've disgraced the profession.)

666
00:33:31,728 --> 00:33:33,327
(This reporter is seeking attention.)

667
00:33:33,367 --> 00:33:33,807
(This is blatantly unconscionable.)

668
00:33:33,807 --> 00:33:34,167
(She made baseless reports,)

669
00:33:34,167 --> 00:33:35,127
(and caused the director
to jump off the building.)

670
00:33:35,367 --> 00:33:36,288
(The baby is born prematurely too.)

671
00:33:36,367 --> 00:33:38,528
Compensate our loss!

672
00:33:38,928 --> 00:33:40,728
Give me back the nursing home!

673
00:34:05,807 --> 00:34:06,288
Xu Lai.

674
00:34:06,688 --> 00:34:07,367
Can you hear me?

675
00:34:11,528 --> 00:34:12,048
Xu Lai.

676
00:34:13,167 --> 00:34:13,888
Can you hear me?

677
00:34:58,287 --> 00:34:58,928
You're awake.

678
00:35:03,687 --> 00:35:04,928
You passed out

679
00:35:05,167 --> 00:35:06,207
because you're running out of air.

680
00:35:09,127 --> 00:35:09,808
Are you feeling unwell now?

681
00:35:11,247 --> 00:35:12,207
Do you want to go to the hospital?

682
00:35:22,448 --> 00:35:22,888
Don't be like that.

683
00:35:24,408 --> 00:35:25,287
If possible,

684
00:35:26,928 --> 00:35:28,207
I'd rather be the one suffering.

685
00:35:34,167 --> 00:35:35,127
I'm sorry.

686
00:35:38,328 --> 00:35:39,207
Don't say that.

687
00:35:41,008 --> 00:35:42,448
Didn't we agree before?

688
00:35:44,127 --> 00:35:45,368
No matter what difficulties we face,

689
00:35:46,247 --> 00:35:47,368
we'll stand together

690
00:35:47,767 --> 00:35:48,607
and solve them.

691
00:35:51,448 --> 00:35:52,207
Let it out.

692
00:35:53,647 --> 00:35:54,727
Don't keep it inside.

693
00:35:55,767 --> 00:35:56,888
It'll feel better if you cry.

694
00:35:58,488 --> 00:36:00,247
It's not the time to cry now.

695
00:36:07,808 --> 00:36:09,368
I can't be brought down just like this.

696
00:36:09,848 --> 00:36:11,687
I have many things to do.

697
00:36:15,647 --> 00:36:16,567
Hug me again.

698
00:36:46,968 --> 00:36:47,567
Hello.

699
00:36:48,008 --> 00:36:49,247
Is there any new progress
on the reconstruction

700
00:36:49,247 --> 00:36:51,008
of Nanxiang Nursing Home?

701
00:36:52,848 --> 00:36:53,368
Thank you.

702
00:37:12,247 --> 00:37:12,848
Compensate our loss!

703
00:37:13,048 --> 00:37:14,687
Compensate our loss!

704
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:46,720
(Call for Action: Elderly People Have
Expectations for Welfare Institutions)

705
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:48,740
(Caring for the elderly
requires action.)

706
00:38:08,928 --> 00:38:09,528
Coming.

707
00:38:17,448 --> 00:38:18,207
What brings you here?

708
00:38:18,727 --> 00:38:19,888
Why didn't you answer the call?

709
00:38:19,888 --> 00:38:20,727
I was sleeping.

710
00:38:21,247 --> 00:38:22,767
I have good news for you.

711
00:38:23,767 --> 00:38:24,607
What's it about?

712
00:38:25,127 --> 00:38:26,567
I went to the nursing home.

713
00:38:27,207 --> 00:38:28,567
They told me the government

714
00:38:28,567 --> 00:38:29,448
has initiated the reconstruction

715
00:38:29,448 --> 00:38:30,928
of Nanxiang Nursing Home.

716
00:38:31,968 --> 00:38:33,528
The elderly's care issue has been solved.

717
00:38:33,528 --> 00:38:34,928
You can rest assured now.

718
00:38:35,127 --> 00:38:35,848
Really?

719
00:38:39,767 --> 00:38:40,567
Ms. Zheng has woken up too.

720
00:38:41,528 --> 00:38:42,368
Let's go and visit her.

721
00:38:42,528 --> 00:38:43,008
Let's go.

722
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:51,760
(Discipline)

723
00:38:51,767 --> 00:38:52,528
Come on, Mighty.

724
00:38:53,567 --> 00:38:53,968
Go.

725
00:38:55,448 --> 00:38:55,928
Zhang Yang.

726
00:38:57,167 --> 00:38:57,488
Here you are.

727
00:38:57,528 --> 00:38:58,368
I've been looking for you.

728
00:38:58,647 --> 00:38:59,048
Looking for me?

729
00:38:59,408 --> 00:39:00,087
What do you want?

730
00:39:01,567 --> 00:39:02,767
You were in the logistic before, right?

731
00:39:03,408 --> 00:39:04,207
You were always watching

732
00:39:04,207 --> 00:39:05,048
the cook there.

733
00:39:05,607 --> 00:39:06,567
You must've learned a lot, right?

734
00:39:07,287 --> 00:39:08,488
Yes, indeed.

735
00:39:09,048 --> 00:39:09,448
What's the matter?

736
00:39:10,647 --> 00:39:12,848
Can you teach me how to cook?

737
00:39:13,607 --> 00:39:14,247
It doesn't have to be complicated.

738
00:39:14,647 --> 00:39:15,928
Just a few simple home-cooked dishes.

739
00:39:17,848 --> 00:39:19,207
Why do you suddenly
want to learn cooking?

740
00:39:20,848 --> 00:39:23,167
Zang Qiu always skips meals

741
00:39:24,247 --> 00:39:25,127
and she has a stomach problem.

742
00:39:25,848 --> 00:39:26,848
As a responsible

743
00:39:27,008 --> 00:39:28,567
and caring man,

744
00:39:29,368 --> 00:39:30,287
I should learn to cook

745
00:39:30,567 --> 00:39:31,408
and take good care of her.

746
00:39:32,368 --> 00:39:33,968
You commit yourself to cooking

747
00:39:34,247 --> 00:39:35,287
just because you want to impress her.

748
00:39:35,567 --> 00:39:37,207
This is so futile.

749
00:39:37,448 --> 00:39:39,448
All you think about is
that doctor every day.

750
00:39:39,848 --> 00:39:40,647
You're a crude man.

751
00:39:40,808 --> 00:39:41,528
You know nothing.

752
00:39:41,647 --> 00:39:41,928
You...

753
00:39:42,008 --> 00:39:42,488
Listen,

754
00:39:42,808 --> 00:39:44,567
I'm being considerate,
attentive, and romantic.

755
00:39:45,888 --> 00:39:47,167
Look at Mighty.

756
00:39:48,287 --> 00:39:49,087
It's way better than you.

757
00:39:49,408 --> 00:39:50,408
You better not end up being alone.

758
00:39:50,687 --> 00:39:51,727
Not even the dogs like you.

759
00:39:52,727 --> 00:39:53,767
Lu Fangqi.

760
00:39:54,287 --> 00:39:54,727
Come here.

761
00:39:55,687 --> 00:39:56,127
The two of you.

762
00:40:00,167 --> 00:40:01,488
What else do I need?

763
00:40:03,928 --> 00:40:04,488
Lu Fangqi.

764
00:40:04,968 --> 00:40:06,008
I didn't expect this though.

765
00:40:06,567 --> 00:40:07,448
I thought

766
00:40:07,848 --> 00:40:09,287
we were doing this in the canteen.

767
00:40:09,888 --> 00:40:11,087
I didn't expect you
to rent a restaurant.

768
00:40:11,808 --> 00:40:12,408
This is the restaurant

769
00:40:12,528 --> 00:40:13,727
where Zang Qiu and I first met.

770
00:40:13,928 --> 00:40:15,247
We happened to save a customer before.

771
00:40:15,607 --> 00:40:17,207
The owner was grateful to us.

772
00:40:18,167 --> 00:40:19,247
The restaurant is closed today,

773
00:40:19,408 --> 00:40:20,528
so I rented it.

774
00:40:22,528 --> 00:40:23,287
How do I make
stir-fried pork with pepper?

775
00:40:23,808 --> 00:40:24,488
Cut the green pepper.

776
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:29,650
♪Memories spark at night♪

777
00:40:29,730 --> 00:40:33,110
♪How do I deal with
the sparks hitting my heart?♪

778
00:40:33,200 --> 00:40:39,260
♪I can't say all the greetings
in my mouth♪

779
00:40:40,250 --> 00:40:46,840
♪I want to ask you later
if you really did let everything go♪

780
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:53,860
♪Do the wounds
from the past still hurt?♪

781
00:40:54,650 --> 00:40:58,870
♪The words that are not true♪

782
00:40:58,870 --> 00:41:02,390
♪Still punishes the ears♪

783
00:41:03,607 --> 00:41:04,167
(Martyr Fang Huai)
Fang Huai.

784
00:41:06,247 --> 00:41:07,008
(Martyr Fang Huai)
I'm here for you.

785
00:41:08,888 --> 00:41:11,087
I never realized how fast time flies.

786
00:41:13,408 --> 00:41:14,848
The scene you gave me flowers

787
00:41:15,008 --> 00:41:16,488
feels like it just happened yesterday.

788
00:41:18,647 --> 00:41:19,488
I often think about

789
00:41:19,647 --> 00:41:21,127
the days when we were together.

790
00:41:23,848 --> 00:41:24,687
So, I always force myself

791
00:41:24,848 --> 00:41:25,687
to get tied up with work.

792
00:41:27,767 --> 00:41:29,247
So I won't think of you.

793
00:41:31,607 --> 00:41:32,448
But recently,

794
00:41:37,968 --> 00:41:39,008
I've realized

795
00:41:40,247 --> 00:41:41,567
that I'm starting to forget
what you looked like.

796
00:41:45,968 --> 00:41:46,928
I have to struggle

797
00:41:48,607 --> 00:41:49,567
to recall many things

798
00:41:49,808 --> 00:41:50,808
and to bring them back to me.

799
00:41:54,127 --> 00:41:55,127
And that makes me realize

800
00:41:56,888 --> 00:41:58,567
that you've left for a long time.

801
00:42:04,888 --> 00:42:05,408
Fang Huai.

802
00:42:06,968 --> 00:42:07,888
I'm really scared.

803
00:42:10,167 --> 00:42:11,448
I'm scared that I'd forget you.

804
00:42:14,727 --> 00:42:15,448
If...

805
00:42:19,328 --> 00:42:19,928
If that

806
00:42:19,968 --> 00:42:21,087
really happens one day,

807
00:42:25,087 --> 00:42:26,119
will you forgive me?

808
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:32,160
♪We are in each other's hearts but
we only care about leaving on our own♪

809
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:37,950
♪It's my fault for missing out
on so much about you♪

810
00:42:38,287 --> 00:42:38,767
Yes?

811
00:42:45,048 --> 00:42:45,607
What?

812
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:52,430
♪The light in the flame♪

813
00:42:52,430 --> 00:42:56,200
♪It's where time sinks in♪

814
00:42:56,800 --> 00:43:01,600
♪It guides me in♪

815
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:06,630
♪I wish to tell you my woes♪

816
00:43:06,770 --> 00:43:10,270
♪So my faith can be whole♪

817
00:43:10,730 --> 00:43:17,000
♪I stand unwavering right next to you♪

818
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:21,330
♪I will be the light♪

819
00:43:21,330 --> 00:43:24,850
♪To show you the path♪

820
00:43:24,970 --> 00:43:28,070
♪Overcoming the perils that come to pass♪

821
00:43:28,670 --> 00:43:32,530
♪Searching for the traces you left behind♪

822
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:35,660
♪I will be the light♪

823
00:43:35,670 --> 00:43:39,200
♪To find a way into your heart♪

824
00:43:39,200 --> 00:43:49,250
♪Fearlessly, I run toward you♪

825
00:43:53,230 --> 00:43:56,810
♪Through the crowds♪

826
00:44:01,670 --> 00:44:04,570
♪The shine in those eyes♪

827
00:44:04,570 --> 00:44:08,170
♪It paused time♪

828
00:44:08,930 --> 00:44:13,530
♪It guides me in♪

829
00:44:16,030 --> 00:44:18,830
♪I wish I could tell you my woes♪

830
00:44:18,830 --> 00:44:22,460
♪To have things I can hold onto♪

831
00:44:22,800 --> 00:44:29,450
♪I stand persevered right next to you♪

832
00:44:30,400 --> 00:44:33,400
♪I will be the light♪

833
00:44:33,400 --> 00:44:36,530
♪To show you the path♪

834
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:40,160
♪Overcoming the perils that come to pass♪

835
00:44:40,730 --> 00:44:44,730
♪Searching for the traces you left behind♪

836
00:44:44,830 --> 00:44:47,890
♪You're the light in my life♪

837
00:44:47,890 --> 00:44:51,330
♪That is shining so bright♪

838
00:44:51,330 --> 00:45:01,730
♪Life goes on, my search continues♪

839
00:45:05,330 --> 00:45:09,730
(Adapted from the novel "Shi Guang Ru Yue"
of Jinjiang Literature City by Xiao Lu)

840
00:45:11,770 --> 00:45:16,610
♪I run toward you♪
